        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "\"The mesh network has also the potential to catalyse many location-specific, occupation-specific smaller networks. One of these offshoots that we are currently thinking about is creating a new network of women. We are thinking of facilitating streams of conversations in the kitchen, of traditional cuisines and knowledge held by women which often do not make it to the public sphere.\"",
